    <div class="container content-text page-sub">
        <p>The headline story of fiscal 2016 is the introduction of a new Johnson Controls. The merger with Tyco strengthens our global leadership in building and energy technologies and solutions, uniquely positioning us to create smarter, safer, more efficient buildings and cities, powered by intelligent, sustainable energy solutions.</p>
<p>As our planet increasingly becomes one community, one network of marketplaces, one inclusive and circular economy, Johnson Controls is doing what we&rsquo;ve always done&mdash;and what we do best: Creating the infrastructure for opportunity. Developing platforms for passionate living. Advancing energies to fuel the future. With a dedication to excellence and a commitment to helping our customers win, we&rsquo;re building tomorrow&mdash;today.</p>
